            "title": "印度相關超級油輪測試霍爾木茲海峽封鎖以緩解國內燃料危機",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sO4UvAAB1z_zeX6UZC_B_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC210AM_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 一艘與印度相關的超級油輪目前正嘗試進行高風險的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>穿越行動,這標誌著新德里為緩解日益惡化的國內能源短缺所做的關鍵努力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博社首次報導,這艘懸掛馬紹爾群島旗幟、載有45,000噸液化石油氣(LPG)的Sarv Shakti號,於週六被觀察到正穿越該水道前往阿曼灣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在InvestingPro上獲取即時能源市場警報</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>美國封鎖下的突破性穿越</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Sarv Shakti號的航行代表了自美國對伊朗相關航運實施封鎖以來,首次觀察到與印度相關的油輪嘗試駛出該海峽。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-56e6e94e-4f06-3e08-ae61-8215b1e90a7b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">船舶追蹤數據顯示,該船在經過伊朗的拉拉克島和格什姆島時,正在廣播其印度船員身份,這是當前衝突期間常見的安全協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這批由國營印度石油公司(IOC)購買的貨物,對於一個正在與烹飪燃料嚴重短缺作鬥爭的國家來說至關重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自4月伊朗軍隊向試圖穿越短暫重新開放的航道的船隻開火以來,霍爾木茲海峽的交通幾乎陷入停滯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度已通過與德黑蘭的雙邊談判成功協商了8艘液化石油氣船隻的通行,但這次最新的穿越是封鎖開始以來規模最大的之一。據報導,Sarv Shakti號在開始穿越之前,已在杜拜外海通過船對船轉運方式接收了貨物。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>印度國內能源危機與應對措施</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為全球第二大液化石油氣消費國,印度受到中東生產商供應缺口的嚴重衝擊。短缺引發了恐慌性購買,並迫使國內消費者減少使用量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為回應,印度政府已下令其港口優先處理液化石油氣油輪,並積極提升國內產量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據石油部長哈迪普·普里(Hardeep Puri)表示,印度已將國內液化石油氣產量提高60%至54,000噸以彌補缺口。然而,即使需求略微下降至每天80,000噸,每日消費量仍超過供應量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Sarv Shakti號的成功駛出將提供暫時的緩解,但霍爾木茲海峽通道持續的不穩定性仍對印度的能源安全和通脹目標構成重大風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%AA%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E4%BB%A5%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-093403502.html",
